<title>24Shopping</title>
<content>

Scotton no longer has a shop or Post Office. The shop at Moorcock Hall Farm has now closed. The village public house now sells basic groceries and both holiday parks have small shops.&lt;br />&lt;br />However it is now possible to shop online and have all your purchases delivered. &lt;br />&lt;br />   &lt;br />
Paul Wilson</content>
